[Course_Description]
Have you wondered how you can be more creative and sustain that spark throughout your organization? Creative principles like imagination, innovation, and play enhance a business's productivity, competitiveness, and the bottom line; yet they may be easier said than done. In this course, Thea Polancic shares concrete steps you can take immediately to strengthen creativity within yourself, your team, and your organization. Thea digs into the nature of creativity and what's required for it to flourish in organizational settings. She shares how to encourage a growth mindset, leverage feedback as the gateway to learning, and eliminate organizational barriers to creativity. Plus, she shares the surprising way that accountability can be a key part of delivering creative results.